Nail A. HARRY, Petitioner,
v.
Mark S. INCH, Secretary, Department of Corrections, Respondent. No. 1D18-3976 District Court of Appeal of Florida, First District. February 25, 2019 Nail A. Harry, pro se, Petitioner. Ashley B. Moody, Attorney General, Tallahassee. Per Curiam.

The petition for writ of habeas corpus is denied on the merits.

Lewis, Winsor, and M.K. Thomas, JJ., concur.
